  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "2002-06-26", 
    "text": "Public Safety Tax Cut Act - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) provide a $1,000 tax credit for full-time police officers and firefighters; and (2) exclude from gross income the value of any public services benefits (water, sewer, trash pickup, and other similar services) received by a public safety volunteer (a volunteer firefighter or volunteer auxiliary police officer)."
